                }
                else {
                    $(".image_thumb ul li:first-child").click();
                }
            }
            else {
                $(".image_thumb ul li.active").next('li').click();
            }
        }

        var Scroll = setInterval(newsRotation, Interval);

        $("#newsRotator").hover(function() {
            clearInterval(Scroll);
        }, function() {
            Scroll = setInterval(newsRotation, Interval);
        });
    });
</script>
